@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 12

title OCI Image Volumes - AI/ML Workflows (K8s 1.31 Alpha)

package "Container Registry" as registry #E6E6FA {
  artifact "ml-model:v2.1\n(2 GB)" as model #FFD700
  artifact "training-data:latest\n(50 GB)" as data #FFD700
  artifact "config:prod\n(10 MB)" as config #FFD700
}

package "Kubernetes Pod" as pod #90EE90 {
  rectangle "ML Training Container" as container {
    folder "/models" as models_dir
    folder "/data" as data_dir
    folder "/config" as config_dir
  }

  rectangle "Volumes OCI" as volumes #87CEEB {
    component "model-volume" as mv
    component "data-volume" as dv
    component "config-volume" as cv
  }
}

model -down-> mv : pull
data -down-> dv : pull
config -down-> cv : pull

mv -right-> models_dir : mount
dv -right-> data_dir : mount
cv -right-> config_dir : mount

note bottom of pod
  **Avantages:**
  ✅ Versioning natif (tags)
  ✅ Cache des layers
  ✅ Distribution globale (CDN)
  ✅ Sécurité (signatures, scanning)
  ✅ Pas besoin de PVC

  **Cas d'usage AI/ML:**
  • Modèles pré-entraînés
  • Datasets de référence
  • Configurations immutables
end note

note right of registry
  **Spec Pod:**
  ```yaml
  volumes:
  - name: model
    image:
      reference: registry/ml-model:v2.1
      pullPolicy: IfNotPresent
  containers:
  - volumeMounts:
    - name: model
      mountPath: /models
  ```
end note

legend right
  |= Type contenu |= Exemple |
  | Modèles ML | TensorFlow, PyTorch |
  | Données | Datasets, embeddings |
  | Config | Paramètres, secrets |
endlegend

@enduml
